id=lite-mem
name=Lite Mem (zram + debloat)
version=v1.1.0
versionCode=2
author=kaandikec
description=Memory relief for the low-RAM ZTE F50 (~1.4GB). Adds an extra zstd-compressed zram swap, raises vm.swappiness/vfs_cache_pressure, disables background bloat (ZTE analytics/neopush/zdm/aftersale/flagreset), and offers a shell-toggleable kill of the ZTE goform web panel (com.zte.web) to save ~25-30MB + stop its telemetry. CLI: `lite-mem status`, `lite-mem webui off|on`. Frees real RAM so V2rayTun/AdGuard stop getting LMK-killed. Fully reversible. Edit /data/lite-mem/bloat.list to customize.
updateJson=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dikeckaan/magisk-zte-f50-lite-mem/main/update.json
